<br>
Religion had no meaning when I rolled my Ogre, but after deciding to play him again after half a year, I now find that VI(after 3years) has finally made it a factor.  Especially for those of us who are unguilded, with no way to get Velious Armor.  I would love to be able to do a quest, even a lenthy one, if it meant I could worship RZ.<br>
<br>
If, and when any info arises please post it here, for those of us in the same boat.<br>
